{"tid":798310,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"新垣結衣沒了雙眼皮變大臉妹    日本網友震驚：悲報！","createTime":"2018-08-29T08:11:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-30T02:34:06.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"412cd0ae24047dd4b129a51c59013b0546434bac","tid":798310,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T08:11:25.000Z","msg":"日本女星新垣結衣去年因電視劇《月薪嬌妻》，人氣再攀高峰，清純模樣更成為台日網友心中的「國民老婆」；早前新垣結衣在節目中表演一秒變成單眼皮的特技，瞬間判若兩臉直接成了普妹，日本網友更以「悲報」為標題，形容內心的悲痛錯愕。<br />\n<br />\n新垣結衣在節目中展現一秒變成單眼皮特技，少了雙眼皮的她，竟然直接變成路人，日本網友看了傻眼吐槽「雙眼皮是正義」、「變普了」 、「臉瞬間變大一圈」、「失去明星光芒」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2018/08/29/2534233_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2018%2F08%2F29%2F2534233_1.jpg&h=d7379e22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新垣結衣示範一秒變成單眼皮特技，一秒即刻變成普妹。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2018/08/29/2534233_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2018%2F08%2F29%2F2534233_2.jpg&h=59b899c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新垣結衣變回雙眼皮後，網友表示欣慰。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2534233\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2534233&d=Y6%2BhmZRuZm2cBO01iDldphv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=4eb027a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2534233&h=d93af0d1\" target=\"_blank\">http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2534233</a>"},{"pid":"924639efa2f3003f463a6e14b5ad3b8cef5fc961","tid":798310,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T08:12:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"545954564b395748da1cb6d3b8c40db895347cab","tid":798310,"uid":68902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T08:24:06.000Z","msg":"結衣BB <img src=\"